  m_Name: MilitaryRecord_10
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::JournalData
  id: 46
  title: "B\xE1o c\xE1o qu\xE2n \u0111\u1ED9i #10 \u2014 K\u1EBF ho\u1EA1ch ph\xE1
    c\u1EA7u"
  category: 5
  content: "M\u1EACT \u2014 K\u1EBE HO\u1EA0CH PH\xC1 C\u1EA6U. Ng\xE0y 19/3. C\u1EA7u
    v\u01B0\u1EE3t n\u1ED1i khu chung c\u01B0 v\u1EDBi b\u1EDD b\xEAn kia l\xE0 tuy\u1EBFn
    \u0111\u01B0\u1EDDng duy nh\u1EA5t c\xF2n l\u1EA1i. N\u1EBFu d\u1ECBch b\u1EC7nh
    lan sang b\u1EDD b\xEAn kia, to\xE0n b\u1ED9 khu v\u1EF1c ph\xEDa nam s\u1EBD
    m\u1EA5t. K\xEDp c\xF4ng binh \u0111\xE3 g\u1EAFn 8 charges \u1EDF tr\u1EE5 ch\xEDnh.
    K\u1EBF ho\u1EA1ch: k\xEDch n\u1ED5 sau khi to\xE0n b\u1ED9 qu\xE2n \u0111\u1ED9i
    r\xFAt xong (d\u1EF1 ki\u1EBFn 23:00 ng\xE0y 19/3). Tuy nhi\xEAn, b\u1ED9 k\xEDch
    n\u1ED5 \u0111\xE3 \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c giao cho m\u1ED9t \u0111\u1ED9i vi\xEAn
    \u2014 \u0111\u1ED9i vi\xEAn n\xE0y m\u1EA5t t\xEDch sau khi b\u1ECB c\u1EAFn.
    C\u1EA7n t\xECm b\u1ED9 k\xEDch n\u1ED5 tr\u01B0\u1EDBc 24 gi\u1EDD, n\u1EBFu
    kh\xF4ng charges s\u1EBD t\u1EF1 \u0111\u1ED9ng k\xEDch ho\u1EA1t theo h\u1EB9n.
    K\xFD: \u0110\u1EA1i t\xE1 Morrison."
  image: {fileID: 0}
  voiceLog: {fileID: 0}
